title: Swallow Your Bliss
writer: Brian Everingham, Pattie Kelly, Phil Scarpaci, Denise Vivaldo
actors: Eva LaRue, Michael Dorn, Lisa Long, Chalet Lizette Brannan
plot: A tantalizing sitcom about a TV cooking show and its life addled crew. In Bliss, the only thing sacred is the food. Everything else is fair game.
